MODEL SELECTION

In this work, we decided to use linear regression, random forest, lasso regression and tree model. When we examined the dataset, it is seem that there is not any production from 20 pm to 5 am for all days. Therefore, we decided to train and predict observations from 5 am to 20 pm.

LINEAR REGRESSION

We conducted linear regression. Firstly, we trained the model. Then, we calculated Mean Absolute Error on training data. After, we made a prediction on test dataset and calculated Mean Square Error on test data set. We did this for all hours.

TREE MODEL
